00:11:58.858 --> 00:11:59.830
Yes?

00:11:59.830 --> 00:12:01.531
AUDIENCE: I don't if
this is maybe just

00:12:01.531 --> 00:12:04.190
my accent's not very good,
but in the bottom left graph--

00:12:04.190 --> 00:12:04.690
Right?

