time-dependent perturbation

00:45:46.010 --> 00:45:47.330
theory.

00:45:47.330 --> 00:45:51.000
Often when this-- when textbooks
treat spontaneous emission,

00:45:51.000 --> 00:45:52.980
they're more interested
