01:10:59.060 --> 01:11:02.640
quadratically, but this part
is a coherent evolution.

01:11:02.640 --> 01:11:06.290
And that's related to the fact
that an atom can emit a photon,

01:11:06.290 --> 01:11:09.985
but in the very first
moment, before the vacuum

01:11:09.985 --> 01:11:13.330
has transported it away, it
can take the photon back.

01:11:13.330 --> 01:11:16.250
And the result of that is
