01:11:42.450 --> 01:11:46.980
but sufficiently large, that we
are not getting into any memory

01:11:46.980 --> 01:11:49.044
affects of the reservoir.

01:11:49.044 --> 01:11:50.710
And we've done the
same assumption here.

